0011|*selects the path of another inquiry system.
0012|*In Survo several inquiry systems may be maintained and used paral-
0013|*lelly provided that different paths are provided for them. The path for
0014|*the default inquiry system is given in the system file SURVO.APU as
0015|*qpath=<default path> (qpath=C:\E\Q\EDQ for example). The three last
S   |       <            >
0016|*characters (EDQ in the example) refer to a common forepart of all file
0017|*names of the inquiry system and they are all standard edit files.
0018|*The root file consisting of the keywords and their references to
0019|*inquiry file has the name EDQ.EDT (or corresponding).
0020|*To see the structure of various inquiry files, examine them, please.
0022|*The QPATH operation can be used to change the inquiry system temporarily.
